messages.content:
Want inspiration for a meme or piece of content to make? Here are our requests and ideas... 

All rewards are subject to the final product being approved by us for quality. We don't give away Points for nothing 🙂 And *most* bounties can only be claimed once.

Submit answers in #📦002-003-breaking-up-with-your-bank-physical-piece-be-of-art with the appropriate tag as mentioned in the bounty.
Pinned a message.

🏆 Won by @Saurois: https://discordapp.com/channels/768556386404794448/803425523563888710/818022435236085780

🖼 NFT: https://rarible.com/token/0xf0ccc03db1adea71598bdad5ea6d869204c467d2:2:0x1309513791c6d34993444bbe135fdbe686ebe33b

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 001** 
*Reward:* 1500 points
*Live:* March 6-7th, 2021

*Description:* Make an Eco-themed version of https://www.kapwing.com/explore/300-what-is-your-profession-spartan-subtitles-meme — make sure to incorporate key ideas about Eco

🏆 Won by @cooloNe: https://discordapp.com/channels/768556386404794448/803425523563888710/818107166438326303
 
**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 002**
*Reward:* 750 points
*Live:* March 6-9th, 2021

*Description:* Make a high-quality video meme based on the theme "breaking up with your bank" and tag it #bounty002

🏆 Won by @mortalwork: https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/818148481520500776/818511540239859732
**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 003**
*Reward:* 500 points
*Live:* March 8-10th, 2021

*Description:* Create a _physical_ piece of content about Eco — a drawing, painting, sculpture, or something else. Be creative! And tag it #bounty003.

(Bounty idea inspired by @SS)

🏆 Won by @cooloNe: https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/818902069036449822/819271292355477535

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 004**
*Reward:* 500 points
*Live:* March 9-10th, 2021

*Description:* Create a short, high-quality video revealing Eco's logo and celebrating the launch of this Discord community. Perhaps incorporate both the Eco logo and the Discord logo, or something else from this community. Submit to #📦004-eco-discord-launch-video.

🏆 Won by @mustachi: https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/819274827666817065/819357685421441025

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 005**
*Reward:* 50-750 points if accepted, depending on quality
*Issued:* March 10th, 2021

*Description:* Make a new emoji for the Eco Discord. Be creative! Some examples already... :eco_deal_with_it: :eco_parrot: :eco_nails: :eco_heart:  :eco_fr: :eco_cat: :eco_100:... Submit to #📦005-eco-emojis

🏆 Won by @Angry: https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/819602547597246534/820829682843910165

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 006**
*Reward:* 500-3000 points if accepted, depending on quality
*Issued:* March 11th, 2021
*Deadline:* March 15th, 2021 evening US Eastern Time (this is a hard one, so long deadline!)

*Description:* Big challenge :eco_deal_with_it:  Build a *Rube Goldberg Machine* that **destroys one of your credit cards** in the most creative way possible. :Scissors:🔥💥🚚 🪓

Examples of Rube Goldberg Machines: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=rube+goldberg+machine

Submit to #📦006-rube-goldberg-machine

🏆  Won by @cooloNe: 
https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/820482778260045874/821082639590359090

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 007**
*Reward*: 100-1000 points if accepted, depending on quality
*Issued*: March 14th, 2021
*Deadline*:  March 18th 2021, 12pm EST

*Description*: For this one we're going virtual, put Eco (Logos, A Mascot or something new) into your favorite virtual community! We're thinking Game Mods, Player Skins, Virtual Art and the like.
I know that games like VRchat and Garry's Mod let you import your own models, games like Super Mario Maker or Dreams let you make levels, Minecraft and others have plenty of ways to do Art or custom Textures.

Won by @cooloNe 

Submit to #📦007-eco-in-the-metaverse

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 008**
*Reward*: 50-750 points if accepted, depending on quality
*Issued*: March 17th, 2021
*Deadline*:  March 21th 2021, 11:59pm EST

*Description*: Make the largest physical Eco logo you can! Include a scale so we know just how big the logo is. Get creative, try mapping it out in fields, on buildings, the sky's the limit.

Submit to #📦008-largest-physical-logo

🏆 Won by @mustachi  https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/824037242452181012/825113589434155018 

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 009**
Reward: 50-800 points if accepted, depending on quality
Issued: March 23th, 2021
Deadline:  March 26th 2021, 11:59pm EST

Description: Design, Draw or Dress up as an Original Eco mascot! Include the Eco Colors, Logo, Attitude or Spirit in your design. I will post some examples of other community mascots for inspiration

Submit to #📦009-eco-mascot

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 010**
Reward: 50-500 points if accepted, depending on quality
Issued: March 26th, 2021
Deadline:  March 29th 2021, 11:30pm EDT

Description: Grab an Eco Sign and Film yourself doing your favorite dance. We are planning to edit them all together at the end into a showcase of the Eco community. 🎵 🕺 

Submit to #📦010-eco-dance-competition

🏆  Won by @w124eth  https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/826238960845324328/827633364738899978

Issued: March 29th, 2021
Deadline:  April 3rd 2021, 11:30pm EDT

Description: Contributed by @palm - Create an eco ‘jingle’ (musical composition / melody) that just sounds... eco  

Submit to #📦011-music-jingle

Reward: 50-400 points if accepted, depending on quality
Issued: April 1st, 2021
Deadline:  April 7th 2021, 11:30pm EDT

Description: Create a four panel Comic, describing what the future would look like with Eco. Inspired by @IgreX 

Submit to #📦012-4-panel

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 013**
Reward: 250-1000 points per acceptable submission
Issued: April 7th, 2021
Deadline: 10 rewarded submissions or 2 weeks from now (21st April) whichever comes first

Description: Get an **Eco tattoo**.  For this bounty we will be rewarding every real and acceptable submission we get, to reflect the amount of commitment

Submit to #📦013-tattoo

🏆 Won by @w124eth https://discord.com/channels/768556386404794448/831284144226041896/832626386358239312

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 014**
Reward: 100-400 points
Issued: April 12th, 2021
Deadline: April 17th 11:30PM EST 2021

Description: Write a Limerick about Eco or its community, be as cheesy or as fun as you want. Limericks follow an 'AABBA' rhyme structure where Lines 1,2 & 5 share a rhyme and are longer than line 3&4 which are usually shorter and share a different rhyme.
I will post some example in the bounty channel.

Submit to #📦014-limerick

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 15**
Reward: up to 3 points per km depending on transport method/quality of result 
Issued: April 20th, 2021
Deadline: April 24th 11:30PM EST 2021

Description: Plot out an Eco logo or image on GPS and log your Run/Walk/Bike/Drive of it. Points allocated based on the quality of the end result, creativity and distance traveled.

Idea credit to @efels 

Submit to #📦015-gps
!grant @efels 15 points for the idea

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 16**
Reward: 300-800 to the winners
Issued: April 25th, 2021
Deadline: May 1st 11:30PM EST 2021

Description: Create a New set of Telegrams stickers for the Eco Community. Points to focus on are: new original designs and designs that help promote the Eco Spirit out in the world and generate interest in the project.

Submit to #📦016-telegram-stickers

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 17**
Reward: up to 1000 for the top 20 Entries
Issued: May 3rd
Deadline: May 10th 11:30PM EST 2021

Description: This is an open-ended bounty, create something with your unique set of skills to celebrate the Eco Discord reaching 20,000 members. Go as far as you wish to go. The top 20 entries will be rewarded.

Submit to #📦017-eco-20k-celebration

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 18**
Reward: 100 - 400 for the winners
Issued: May 14th
Deadline: May 24th 11:30PM EST 2021

Description: For this bounty we would like to see the talents of our Cosplay community. Dress up as an original Eco character or your favorite with an Eco twist  on it.

Submit to #📦018-eco-cosplay

**ECO CONTENT BOUNTY 19**
Reward: 1 point multiplied by the number of users included, per user, capped at 60 members per submission. Entries to be rewards will be selected at our discrection and subject to authentication of each user involved.
Issued: June 3rd
Deadline: June 15th 11:30PM EST 2021

Description: For this bounty we would like to see Cooperation between members of the Eco Community. So for each new User Included in the Bounty the prize rewarded to all will increase. Create a Gif Animation, promoting Eco or its Community. For Each New User added they may create up to 10 additional Frames of Animation.

Make sure to document each member's Contribution and Process.

Submit to #🏹content-bounty-19
